<div id="node-35" class="node">


  <h2><a href="../../node/35" title="Building communities using the Userpoints module and API">Building communities using the Userpoints module and API</a></h2>

  
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-type-text field-field-room"><div class="field-label">Room:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item odd">BA 1240</div></div></div><p><a href="http://drupal.org/project/userpoints">Userpoints</a> is a module that allows users to be awarded points for participating in a web site (e.g. posting content, commenting, ...etc.)</p>
<p>With Userpoints 2.x, a flexible and extensible API has been put in place to allow additional modules to be developed to expand where points can be gained/lost, as well as actions to be performed when points are gained/lost.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block clear">
    <div class="meta">
          <div class="terms"><ul class="links inline"><li  class="first taxonomy_term_4"><a href="4" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_4">Consultants</a></li>
<li  class="taxonomy_term_2"><a href="2" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_2 active">Developers</a></li>
<li  class="last taxonomy_term_3"><a href="3" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_3">Newbies</a></li>
</ul></div>
        </div>

          <div class="links"><ul class="links inline"><li  class="first comment_comments"><a href="../../node/35#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting." class="comment_comments">1 comment</a></li>
